comment:
* Information returned by {@link Os#uname}.
 * Corresponds to C's {@code struct utsname} from {@code <sys/utsname.h>}.

variables.name: nodename
variables.comment: The machine's unqualified name on some implementation-defined network.

variables.name: version
variables.comment: The OS version, such as "#48-Ubuntu SMP Tue Feb 22 20:25:29 UTC 2011".

variables.name: machine
variables.comment: The machine architecture, such as "armv7l" or "x86_64".
